[
  {
    "startTime": 1.599,
    "endTime": 3.36,
    "text": "you are about to hear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.36,
    "endTime": 7.759,
    "text": "a strange but true story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.759,
    "endTime": 10.8,
    "text": "legend has it harry houdini the master"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.8,
    "endTime": 12.08,
    "text": "magician"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.08,
    "endTime": 14.32,
    "text": "once claimed that he could break out of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.32,
    "endTime": 15.519,
    "text": "any jail cell"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.519,
    "endTime": 19.6,
    "text": "in the world all he had to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.6,
    "endTime": 22.64,
    "text": "was walk into that jail cell with his"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.64,
    "endTime": 23.6,
    "text": "street clothes on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.6,
    "endTime": 25.039,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.039,
    "endTime": 27.519,
    "text": "i'll be out of there in one hour no"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.519,
    "endTime": 28.8,
    "text": "problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.8,
    "endTime": 32.398,
    "text": "he said well a very"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.399,
    "endTime": 35.68,
    "text": "old jail down south heard about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.68,
    "endTime": 37.76,
    "text": "houdini's claims"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.76,
    "endTime": 40.719,
    "text": "and they accepted his challenge on the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.719,
    "endTime": 42.239,
    "text": "day of the event"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.239,
    "endTime": 45.68,
    "text": "many people gathered outside"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.68,
    "endTime": 48.559,
    "text": "very confidently houdini walked right"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.559,
    "endTime": 50.399,
    "text": "into the jail"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.399,
    "endTime": 53.84,
    "text": "and into the cell and they shut"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.84,
    "endTime": 58.32,
    "text": "the metal doors behind him"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.32,
    "endTime": 60.96,
    "text": "the first thing houdini did was he took"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.96,
    "endTime": 62.96,
    "text": "off his coat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.96,
    "endTime": 68.24,
    "text": "then very strangely he took off his belt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.24,
    "endTime": 71.28,
    "text": "secretly hidden in houdini's belt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.28,
    "endTime": 74.4,
    "text": "was a 10 inch piece of steel very"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.4,
    "endTime": 78.799,
    "text": "tough and very flexible and houdini"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.799,
    "endTime": 83.04,
    "text": "started working in about 30 minutes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.04,
    "endTime": 85.36,
    "text": "that confident expression houdini had"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.36,
    "endTime": 86.08,
    "text": "when he walked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.08,
    "endTime": 89.36,
    "text": "in disappeared"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.36,
    "endTime": 93.119,
    "text": "in one hour he was bathed in sweat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.119,
    "endTime": 95.759,
    "text": "and at the end of two hours houdini in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.759,
    "endTime": 97.28,
    "text": "defeat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.28,
    "endTime": 101.439,
    "text": "collapsed against the door"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.439,
    "endTime": 105.52,
    "text": "which then opened"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.52,
    "endTime": 108.64,
    "text": "it opened because you see that door had"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.64,
    "endTime": 110.88,
    "text": "never been locked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.88,
    "endTime": 114.079,
    "text": "but that's not entirely true is it that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.079,
    "endTime": 115.52,
    "text": "door was locked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.52,
    "endTime": 119.04,
    "text": "it was firmly and thoroughly locked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.04,
    "endTime": 122.159,
    "text": "in houdini's mind which meant it was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.159,
    "endTime": 122.64,
    "text": "locked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.64,
    "endTime": 125.2,
    "text": "as if the best locksmith in the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.2,
    "endTime": 128.64,
    "text": "had put his lock on it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.64,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "the mind is powerful"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 134.48,
    "text": "how many doors in your life do you think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.48,
    "endTime": 135.52,
    "text": "are locked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.52,
    "endTime": 138.319,
    "text": "but aren't how many times have you been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.319,
    "endTime": 138.959,
    "text": "stuck"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.959,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "in the mental prison of overthinking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 144.56,
    "text": "something that really had a simple"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.56,
    "endTime": 146.879,
    "text": "solution"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.879,
    "endTime": 149.2,
    "text": "there is an ancient african proverb that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.2,
    "endTime": 150.64,
    "text": "says when there is no"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.64,
    "endTime": 154.48,
    "text": "enemy within the enemy outside"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.48,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "can do us no harm your mind"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 161.04,
    "text": "is the most powerful force you will ever"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.04,
    "endTime": 164.4,
    "text": "face it will tell you lies it will tell"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.4,
    "endTime": 164.8,
    "text": "you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.8,
    "endTime": 166.72,
    "text": "you can't do that you're not meant for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.72,
    "endTime": 168.48,
    "text": "that you're not good enough for that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.48,
    "endTime": 170.72,
    "text": "you can't go on anymore you don't have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.72,
    "endTime": 173.2,
    "text": "the energy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.2,
    "endTime": 176.16,
    "text": "you must thank it for its opinion and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.16,
    "endTime": 178.319,
    "text": "carry on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.319,
    "endTime": 181.28,
    "text": "because like houdini showed us the only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.28,
    "endTime": 183.76,
    "text": "locked doors that exist"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.76,
    "endTime": 188.72,
    "text": "or in your own mind the doors in reality"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.72,
    "endTime": 192.879,
    "text": "are open and all you have to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.879,
    "endTime": 199.84,
    "text": "is walk through"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.1,
    "endTime": 208.639,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.59,
    "endTime": 220.879,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.18,
    "endTime": 229.87,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.78,
    "endTime": 251.84,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.84,
    "endTime": 253.92,
    "text": "you"
  }
